2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper specifically deals with multicast coding in relay networks, which is a topic within networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper presents randomized and deterministic polynomial-time versions of the algorithm, which is a topic within data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with multicast coding in networks, which is a topic within social and information networks. 
5. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper presents a deterministic polynomial-time algorithm, which is a topic within computational complexity.
